cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.RO

This paper is primarily focused on deep reinforcement learning (RL) and the use of evolutionary algorithms to learn RL policies directly from pixels. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which encompasses topics related to deep learning and RL. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of novelty search, which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and evolutionary algorithms (cs.NE). The experiments conducted in the paper involve playing Atari games, which fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories.
